{"tid":139914,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇華爾街日報大戰Pewdiepie?","createTime":"2017-03-01T19:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T14:14:45.000Z","uid":20835,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80ba26d7feb1188046605f48acaa8cb6193c064e","tid":139914,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T19:56:52.000Z","msg":"詳情請google"},{"pid":"bd233f8c72201943c2bb1adec11d01ce134ac37e","tid":139914,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T20:09:44.000Z","msg":"報紙佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390e7adf513d2a962fa0e47a508ce4bf7412a24c","tid":139914,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T20:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報紙佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0d6e87087be95d9a94905955728083fda03e51","tid":139914,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T22:03:44.000Z","msg":"diefishfish我就識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601ae15472f27e92fcbcf63e5df00dcdc8f02af1","tid":139914,"uid":44491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T22:22:58.000Z","msg":"failing business <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ab9de6b77e22402bfa4fb0141ce4f0b291b31c","tid":139914,"uid":59835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T22:24:30.000Z","msg":"連登應該多人睇遠哥"},{"pid":"965256eafb9c6098cace5622b3c2a95695402b78","tid":139914,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:00:52.000Z","msg":"WSJ? More like SJW"},{"pid":"2fe1d8b863754bb92f6051674b75f3db456d17c1","tid":139914,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:32:13.000Z","msg":"[wow]"},{"pid":"d3bdc1c1a6df0569432ce4a63c0717d5b81b1925","tid":139914,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>WSJ? More like SJW</blockquote><br />\nI did nazi that meaning hidden"},{"pid":"a4df6ec0037877d5fb318e369cfe5f333ee09d91","tid":139914,"uid":73112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:36:09.000Z","msg":"Loui5Ng伍公子<br />\n<br />\n《我看Pewdiepie》<br />\n<br />\n近來，華爾街日報指責Pewdiepie的影片鼓吹種族仇恨<br />\n<br />\n(<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/www.wsj.com/amp/articles/pewdiepie-says-wsj-took-anti-semitic-content-out-of-context-1487278375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Famp%2Farticles%2Fpewdiepie-says-wsj-took-anti-semitic-content-out-of-context-1487278375&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6Jsf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fa423c77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/www.wsj.com/amp/articles/pewdiepie-says-wsj-took-anti-semitic-content-out-of-context-1487278375</a>)<br />\n<br />\n各界評論不一，以下淺談個人觀感。<br />\n<br />\nPewdiepie是YouTube第一的個人頻道，他資產逾千萬美元，影響力遍及全球。<br />\n<br />\n他成功，因為他堅持創作，個人風格平易近人，作品易於入口。<br />\n<br />\n一段約十分鐘長的遊戲影片，充斥低俗笑話和自嘲謾罵，觀眾不用多加思考。<br />\n<br />\n在我看來，Pewdiepie的成功，既象徵着大眾品味低落，亦象徵着網絡文化的進步。<br />\n<br />\n因為全球一體化是人類必然的方向，而互聯網正好充當人類文化熔爐。<br />\n<br />\n要達到全球文化融合，過程中需要大量磨合，而低俗的網上娛樂正是必經階段。<br />\n<br />\n例如色情網站Pornhub上鮮有網民爭執；Pewdiepie的廣大觀眾來自不同國家，卻以兄弟相稱。<br />\n<br />\n事實證明，網上的低俗娛樂可以令不同國籍的人放下分歧。<br />\n<br />\nPewdiepie頻道背後只是一個普通人，他的影片或許不符你我品味，但他的作品決不可能為帶來世界仇恨，與之相反，我認為他為互聯網帶來和諧。<br />\n<br />\n在我看來，華爾街日報的抨擊子虛烏有，背後是為了打壓網絡聲音，抹殺有影響力的民間代表。<br />\n<br />\n這是一場第四權和第五權的鬥爭。<br />\n<br />\n對此，我重申個人信念：我始終堅信，互聯網文化必須保持自由，不應存在任何形式的限制。<br />\n<br />\n雖然網上充斥各種醜惡，各種陰謀，但是，互聯網亦同時滿載各種美善，這裡必然是人類未來的發祥地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Loui5Ng/posts/1835860589773350:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLoui5Ng%2Fposts%2F1835860589773350%3A0&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6Jsf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c7d6bf8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Loui5Ng/posts/1835860589773350:0</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有超粒方有講，擺明傳統媒體畏懼網絡權力貼影響力大過佢地，而殺一儆百，做假新聞做鳩佢。"},{"pid":"ca23757b588c5792eb49c012a28352d9cdda6542","tid":139914,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:36:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>failing business <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑死, WSJ, NYT, WashPost, 都係好穏陣"},{"pid":"2af70feab6f55d973265b20f9146eda272d86326","tid":139914,"uid":12232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T01:14:09.000Z","msg":"hypofritz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ef02653bba1e9308cdc44cb546c7ca1d5f14db","tid":139914,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T02:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>diefishfish我就識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩 真係好耐冇聽過人講死魚魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6ff882502a81c7edcf610166a7acab28ea846b","tid":139914,"uid":87892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"報紙佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同垃圾TVB一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要刻意斷章取義做到年輕人既喜好潮流全部都係廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢種死老坑廢中真係邊個國家都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c26aedf2d57cba